 reveal the crucial role such images played in shaping modern understandings of conflict.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 22. Okt 2019) 7aART / History / Romanticism.2bisacsh40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300230161423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780300230161.jpg  aGBV-deGruyter-alles